trans-unit.source: Represents the abstract base class for composable part catalogs, which collect and return <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: Representa a classe base abstrata para catálogos de parte de composição, qual coletar e retornar <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartDefinition"> </xref> objetos.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > This type implements the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT]> Este tipo implementa o <xref:System.IDisposable>interface.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: When you have finished using the type, you should dispose of it either directly or indirectly.
trans-unit.target: Quando você terminar de usar o tipo, descarte-direta ou indiretamente.

trans-unit.source: To dispose of the type directly, call its <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A> method in a `try`/`catch` block.
trans-unit.target: Para descartar o tipo diretamente, chame seu <xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>método em um `try` / `catch` bloco.</xref:System.IDisposable.Dispose%2A>

trans-unit.source: To dispose of it indirectly, use a language construct such as `using` (in C#) or `Using` (in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: Para descartar indiretamente dele, use uma construção de linguagem, como `using` (em c#) ou `Using` (no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the “Using an Object that Implements IDisposable” section in the <xref:System.IDisposable> interface topic.
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte a seção "Usando um objeto que implementa IDisposable" o <xref:System.IDisposable>tópico da interface.</xref:System.IDisposable>

trans-unit.source: This type is thread safe.
trans-unit.target: Esse tipo é thread-safe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Releases all resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Libera todos os recursos usados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Call `Dispose` when you are finished using the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>.
trans-unit.target: Chamar `Dispose` quando terminar de usar o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>

trans-unit.source: The `Dispose` method leaves the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog> in an unusable state.
trans-unit.target: O `Dispose` método deixa o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>em um estado inutilizável.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>

trans-unit.source: After calling `Dispose`, you must release all references to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog> so the garbage collector can reclaim the memory that the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog> was occupying.
trans-unit.target: Depois de chamar `Dispose`, você deve liberar todas as referências para o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>para o coletor de lixo possa recuperar a memória que o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>estava ocupando.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog> </xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Cleaning Up Unmanaged Resources](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Implementing a Dispose Method](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte [limpeza de recursos não gerenciados](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) e [implementar um método Dispose](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Always call `Dispose` before you release your last reference to the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > Sempre chamada `Dispose` antes de liberar sua última referência a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>

trans-unit.source: Otherwise, the resources it is using will not be freed until the garbage collector calls the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog> object's `Finalize` method.
trans-unit.target: Caso contrário, os recursos que está usando não serão liberados até que o coletor de lixo chame o <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>do objeto `Finalize` método.</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog>

trans-unit.source: Releases the unmanaged resources used by the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog"></xref> and optionally releases the managed resources.
trans-unit.target: Libera os recursos não gerenciados usados pelo <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.Primitives.ComposablePartCatalog"> </xref> e, opcionalmente, libera os recursos gerenciados.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to release both managed and unmanaged resources; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> to release only unmanaged resources.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>para liberar recursos gerenciados e não gerenciados; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> para liberar apenas recursos não gerenciados.
